    Title: Agamemnon
    By: Aeschylus
    Location: I 177
  Location: Dedication page
By: Aeschylus
---
He who learns must suffer. And even in our sleep pain that cannot forget
falls drop by drop upon the heart, and in our own despair, against our w111,
comes wisdom to us by the awful grace of God.
